Class RetrievalBlock

java.lang.Object
  com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport.RetrievalBlock

public final class RetrievalBlock
extends Object

An collection of RetrievalDatums that together contain all the information necessary for the Intelligence Analysis Platform to retrieve the data for a Card from a particular external source.

4.0
